---
title: Garlic & Herb Mango Beef with Roasted Veggies & Smokey Aioli
description: Here’s a hearty beef bowl that draws inspiration from countless cuisines and brings it straight to your plate. Herby beef strips, coated in a tropical mango-chilli sauce meets roasted veggies tossed with greens, and there’s a dollop of smokey aioli to finish it off.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
